'''Kath Soucie''' is an actress, and a prolific voice actress best known for her portrayal of the fraternal twins Phil and Lil and their mother Betty on the animated show [[Wikipedia:Rugrats|''Rugrats'']], as well as Kanga in [[The Walt Disney Company|Disney]] versions of [[Wikipedia:Winnie the Pooh (franchise)|''Winnie the Pooh'']] since 2000, and Princess Sally Acorn in the 1993 [[Wikipedia:Sonic the Hedgehog (TV series)|''Sonic the Hedgehog'']] cartoon. In relation to ''[[Star Wars]]'', she has provided voice work for several [[Star Wars video games|video game]]s, including ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]'', where she voices the [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Voidhound|Smuggler]], and the animated TV shows ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' and ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]''.

